                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190526-38-off213 t18190526-38-cd214"></join>, 164 lbs. of lead, value 2 l., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190526-38-victim374" type="victimName">
